{"article_id":"hhm8HE4zwuAvf3nQ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"First elected in 1978 ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Baucus has been the top Democrat on the powerful tax-writing committee for more than a dozen years .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"At times infuriating his Democratic colleagues ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"he worked with Republicans","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"to co-write the Bush-era tax cuts and the Medicare prescription drug plan ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"but he also served as the lead defender against George W. Bush ' s 2005 effort","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"to partially privatize Social Security","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"and played a critical role","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"in writing President Obama ' s national health-care plan...","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Despite Obama ' s double-digit defeat in Montana , Democrats intend to vigorously defend the seat .","depth":2},{"id":10,"text":"The leading Democratic candidate is former governor Schweitzer , a popular figure","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"who at times has feuded with Baucus over parochial political issues in the Big Sky state .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"He made news twice last week ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"once for voting against the Democrats ' gun-control bills","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"and the other for warning","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that ObamaCare ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"of which he was a lead architect ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"would be a \" train wreck \"","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"if not implemented properly .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Maybe he hears the train whistle in the distance","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"and figures","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"he ' ll get off the tracks now .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"As for the gun-control votes , two theories .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"One :","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"He really does believe in gun rights .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"He ' s not just pandering to his red-state constituency .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Two :","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"He was fully prepared to run again","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"( he has millions in the bank","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"to fund a campaign ) ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"but something happened between last Wednesday and today","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"to make him suddenly reconsider .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Hmmm .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Normally the retirement of a six-term Democratic incumbent from a conservative state is cause for celebration ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"but I don ' t know .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"When PPP polled Montana two months ago ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Baucus ' s approval was underwater at 45/48 .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Republicans will be out in force next year for the midterms ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"and Baucus hasn ' t had to run a midterm campaign under a Democratic president since his first election in 1978 .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"With ObamaCare hanging over his head ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"he was beatable .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Brian Schweitzer , his likely replacement as Democratic nominee","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"who once said","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"he couldn ' t run for Senate","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"because he ' s not \" senile enough , \"","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"has huge name recognition as governor , a favorable rating of 56/37 per PPP , and none of Baucus ' s Senate baggage","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"( \" Too tied to the Washington special interests , too aloof , too close to the Obama administration \" ) .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Arguably the Democrats are trading up here , to the point","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"where I ' m tempted to wonder","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"if maybe they pushed Baucus out somehow .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Is that even possible , though , with a six-term Senator","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"who ' s written most of the country ' s tax laws ?","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"They ' d have to have some awfully grimy dirt on him .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"And","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"if they did ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"why not drop it on him before the gun votes","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"so that he ' d vote their way ?","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"Update :","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"Via NRO ' s Andrew Stiles ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"here ' s Schweitzer four days ago","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"checking the gun-rights box :","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":121,"left":69,"right":120,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":69,"left":62,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":64,"right":67,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":64,"left":2,"right":63,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":63,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":65,"right":66,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":65,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":9,"right":119,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":119,"left":80,"right":118,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":70,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":76,"right":78,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":12,"right":75,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":13,"right":74,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":14,"right":73,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pare